 * How to build the code
 
 1) Make a main program in 'main' directory.
    - Name the main program as "main_anaHAL.cpp" (or modify 'Makefile' in the directory).
    - You can use "set_main.sh" to create the simbolic link to your own main program.
 
 2) Modify the 'include/Makefile.inc' if necessary.
 
 3) Create a executable file.
    - Do "make" in the top directory.
    - You can find the executable file in 'bin' directory.
 
 Note : Do 'make lib' if you want the library of this code.

=================================================================================
